title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: Upon attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Add a table to the report that has a group with a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row.
3. Preview the report.
4. Attempt to export the data from the table.
5. Verify if an exception is thrown.
